<li><cite style="font-style:normal" class="" id="CITEREFJennifer_Cousineau">Jennifer Cousineau (Spring/Summer 2005). "<a href="http://web.ebscohost.com/ehost/pdf?vid=5&amp;hid=117&amp;sid=befb6f3d-ea2e-4fab-8d18-3253e6d809d3%40sessionmgr3" class="external text" title="http://web.ebscohost.com/ehost/pdf?vid=5&amp;hid=117&amp;sid=befb6f3d-ea2e-4fab-8d18-3253e6d809d3%40sessionmgr3" rel="nofollow">Rabbinic Urbanism in London: Rituals and the Material Culture of the Sabbath</a>". <i>Jewish Social Studies</i> <b>11</b> (3): 36–57. <a href="/wiki/Digital_object_identifier" title="Digital object identifier">doi</a>:<span class="neverexpand"><a href="http://dx.doi.org/10.1353%2Fjss.2005.0021" class="external text" title="http://dx.doi.org/10.1353%2Fjss.2005.0021" rel="nofollow">10.1353/jss.2005.0021</a></span><span class="printonly">. <a href="http://web.ebscohost.com/ehost/pdf?vid=5&amp;hid=117&amp;sid=befb6f3d-ea2e-4fab-8d18-3253e6d809d3%40sessionmgr3" class="external free" title="http://web.ebscohost.com/ehost/pdf?vid=5&amp;hid=117&amp;sid=befb6f3d-ea2e-4fab-8d18-3253e6d809d3%40sessionmgr3" rel="nofollow">http://web.ebscohost.com/ehost/pdf?vid=5&amp;hid=117&amp;sid=befb6f3d-ea2e-4fab-8d18-3253e6d809d3%40sessionmgr3</a></span><span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved on 2007-06-13</span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.atitle=Rabbinic+Urbanism+in+London%3A+Rituals+and+the+Material+Culture+of+the+Sabbath&amp;rft.jtitle=Jewish+Social+Studies&amp;rft.aulast=Jennifer+Cousineau&amp;rft.au=Jennifer+Cousineau&amp;rft.date=Spring%2FSummer+2005&amp;rft.volume=11&amp;rft.issue=3&amp;rft.pages=36%E2%80%9357&amp;rft_id=info:doi/10.1353%2Fjss.2005.0021&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fweb.ebscohost.com%2Fehost%2Fpdf%3Fvid%3D5%26hid%3D117%26sid%3Dbefb6f3d-ea2e-4fab-8d18-3253e6d809d3%2540sessionmgr3&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Eruv"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></s